http://www.thehindu.com/news/national/kerala/Man-killed-in-accident/article13978240.ece

: A 55-year-old man was fatally knocked down by a car at Kallangai in Paivalige panchayat here on Saturday, the police said.The deceased was identified as Somappa Gatti. The accident occurred at 9 a.m. when he was crossing the road. The car was carrying a group of persons from Puthupally in Wayanad who were engaged in implementing the Jalanidhi project in Paivalige panchayat.The man, a resident of Kallangai, succumbed to his injuries in a hospital here, police said adding that a case has been registered in connection with the incident.